# $NAME

FastAPI e-commerce skeleton scaffolded by HarnessX.

Endpoints:

- `GET /healthz` — liveness
- `GET /products`, `GET /products/{id}`
- `GET /cart/{user_id}`, `POST /cart/{user_id}`
- `POST /checkout`

```sh
harness lint
harness test
harness dev
harness ci
```

Storage is in-memory and reset between tests via `conftest.py`. Swap
out `app/storage.py` for a real database when you outgrow the demo.
